{"tid":1465061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣)文宣組 唔想場抗爭因為今日轉為劣勢嘅話 我哋喺時候開工啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:26.000Z","uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b563a8e71610690b1c5bbe0348ab30598c0815b1","tid":1465061,"uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"我明白好多手足認為 民意無用 屌人民意撚 但民意其實對一場運動點都會有作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捉到公安 其實放又唔喺 留又唔喺 <br />\n放咗 聽日政府肯定話條友唔喺公安  <br />\n而唔放嘅話 又會出現而家個問題 喺記者鏡頭前表現得好激進 <br />\n所以港共呢招 真喺好勁 好難拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日機場件事 無可否認會令民意有所動搖 <br />\n亦都好肯定 今晚開始啲藍絲group加埋政府 一定會用呢點大做文章 意圖令民意逆轉 <br />\n所以今次喺文宣戰嘅關鍵 <br />\n<br />\n成件事個畫面出咗街 就一定喺難睇 但有一個事實放在公眾面前 就喺原本暗地裡做嘢嘅公安  <br />\n而家<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光明正大咁企喺示威者入面</span></strong></span> <br />\n呢個做法絕對喺<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共無視一國兩制嘅表現</strong></span></span> 明顯俾示威者放唔放個所謂傷者走更加重要<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋今次嘅文宣 喺唔好俾港共將重點拉去打鬼打公安 重點喺 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港共一直強調嘅一國兩制 而家已被證明 已經唔存在</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7e43ff767e7af1bd5aac6235e618fb68d1c8f56e","tid":1465061,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"岩 一樣諗法 <br />\n<br />\n將個波射番去公安係香港執法啦！"},{"pid":"47f016c73b8746d5083ebc8cccc61baf5180d45b","tid":1465061,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"667239b1d90cd6d448ac433be87e318cb20dae3a","tid":1465061,"uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"推 唔想手足一直以嚟嘅血同汗 俾港共用咁仆街嘅手法搞散<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801cb9ce8febf685301d2bd97de3c5a0c24106ab","tid":1465061,"uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4c0c971f6c3eca18930888fe550c348f6f7cce9","tid":1465061,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.18!!! NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UF14MdG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUF14MdG.jpg&h=b5d28ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPVJhkn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPVJhkn.png&h=8ce1f12e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQ96e62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQ96e62.jpg&h=42fb3e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stPYQFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstPYQFn.jpg&h=b84aa88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93uh6dH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93uh6dH.jpg&h=2269f4db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffd85044d8f3a437c69f54fd7c31b52bfed57554","tid":1465061,"uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6396db86ee2b95a082dd9a5397871e21df4ba7e","tid":1465061,"uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c764050988f56f04917e9fd9b77f3e0fd6d1bee","tid":1465061,"uid":192126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}